# Database Design

## Purpose

This document describes the database structure for the Drone Inspection System.

---

### Drone

- battery_level
- status

### Mission

- mission_id
- drone_id
- inspection_area_id
- start_time
- end_time
- status

### Inspection Area

- inspection_area_id
- name
- beacon_id
- description

### Image

- image_id
- mission_id
- file_path
- timestamp

### AI Detection

- detection_id
- image_id
- object_type
- confidence
- bounding_box

